subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Derek Lamely, a second-year player, shot a nine-under-par 63 in the first round of the Bob Hope Classic in La Quinta, Calif., playing the final 10 holes in eight under for a one-stroke lead over J. J. Henry and Jhonattan Vegas.
